      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "[AI] fix(agents): recover from non-resumable assistant tail by re-presenting last user message",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nAfter gateway restart, sessions with text-only assistant-tail interruptions (no tool calls, no approval pending) failed silently, forcing users to retype their request. The restart recovery code only handled raw API message formats and the physical last message, missing text-only canonical content-block representations and trailing system/compaction messages. This PR recovers from that state by detecting the text-only tail, extracting the last user message from the transcript, and re-presenting it to the agent.\n\nTool-call tails and approval-pending tails remain fail-closed — the broader no-retype recovery policy for side-effecting tails is tracked in #95609.\n\n## Summary\n\n- Problem: Text-only assistant tails after gateway restart forced user retype\n- Solution: Extract last user message from transcript and re-present via `buildResumeMessage()` with idempotency guard\n- Scope: Text-only recovery. Tool-call and approval-pending tails still fail and prompt retype.\n\n## Evidence\n\n51 unit tests pass covering the full recovery pipeline: tool-call detection (6 canonical formats), user message extraction (string + content-block arrays), meaningful tail detection, 200-message fallback, idempotency guard, and text-only fail-closed scope.\n\n```console\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/main-session-restart-recovery.test.ts --run\n\n RUN  v4.1.8\n\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  51 passed (51)\n   Duration  7.73s\n```\n\n## Security Impact\n\n- [x] New permissions/capabilities? No\n- [x] Secrets/tokens handling changed? No\n- [x] New/changed network calls? No\n\n## AI Assistance\n\n- **AI-assisted**: Yes\n- **AI model**: deepseek-v4-pro\n\n---\n\nRelated to #95609\n\n**Scope note**: This PR covers text-only assistant-tail recovery. Broader no-retype policy for remaining tail types stays in #95609.",
